Name: Preformed Coin Wrapper
Description: Keep coins organized with this preformed coin wrapper. Designed to accommodate up to 40 quarters for a total of $10, this item uses 60 lb. grade paper and is color-coded with orange denominations and candy stripes to visually identify its proper function. This convenient product also meets ABA standards to supply you with a convenient wrapper that is bound to increase the efficiency of your coin storage operation. Plus, thanks to its durable double-wrapped kraft construction, this item offers superior security during transport when compared to lighter grade paper options.
